heading_context: Report a flood or possible cause of flooding
chunks.html_content:
Who you need to contact depends on what’s flooding.

Contact your local water company to fix:

  • blocked sewers
  • burst water mains

heading_context: Report a flood or possible cause of flooding
chunks.html_content:
Call the Environment Agency to report:

  • collapsed or badly damaged river banks
  • flooding from main rivers or the sea

  • main rivers blocked by a vehicle or fallen tree causing risk of flooding

  • unusual changes in river flow

Contact your local council to report flooding from other rivers, brooks or streams.
